{"tid":1834086,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊明燉湯店盜用藍象註冊商標 , 泰國總部要求移除相關宣傳","createTime":"2020-01-22T08:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T09:02:52.000Z","uid":25468,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"27e9da1e83d53ea2b3f191443cdd2b1fcf66a03f","tid":1834086,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:50:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/24v8JEeLsTrP_0UNk6A5tLYof3s=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/JL5RRGQK4BONOBSL54OSORBFRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F24v8JEeLsTrP_0UNk6A5tLYof3s%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FJL5RRGQK4BONOBSL54OSORBFRM.jpg&h=b7ab4c61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藝人楊明因高調撐警，網民表明會罷食楊明有份投資的燉湯店，近日燉湯店再遭網民狙擊，指楊明其中一間燉湯店涉嫌違規經營，稱已向食物環境衞生署(食環署)作出舉報，其後食環署發言人回覆《蘋果》如下：「根據記錄，查詢所指位於九龍荔枝角長義街10號昌隆工業大廈地下3號A2舖的處所領有本署簽發的食物製造廠牌照，處所只可配製及出售食物供人在該處所以外進食。本署曾接獲該處所容許有關工廠大廈以外人士光顧的投訴。本署一直留意其情況，並在2019年9月及今年1月發現該處所有人出售膳食供人在該處所內進食，已向有關店鋪負責人以無牌經營食肆罪行提出檢控。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3895478/org/99ddeac30e0ee6fb3546b088df2601e1.jpg/Zukoas9lYETfui41H0kIxDsmay7Ni9ifK4tD0iuLQ9I\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3895478%2Forg%2F99ddeac30e0ee6fb3546b088df2601e1.jpg%2FZukoas9lYETfui41H0kIxDsmay7Ni9ifK4tD0iuLQ9I&h=c38d400a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n狙擊事件當然未有平息，今日FB專頁「專業清算師」發文「燉燉燉燉：和你飛到泰國投訴『燉』盗用藍象商標」，內容如下：「有關昨日藍象公司向『燉』發出聲明一事，我師表示承認責任，並敦促『燉』盡快停止不法侵權行為。乜又係你呀『燉』生？又唔守法喇？今次仲要衰出國際線添呀？做乜要盜用人哋嘅註冊商標呀？咁樣係唔啱㗎！哎呀！唔好意思，啱啱入埋你其餘分店嘅資料畀泰國嘅清算師手足添！支持嚴正執法，打擊盜竊版權！手足下次大家見到口講守法嘅藍店，記得『支持』下佢哋啦！」結果當然有不少網民支持追究任何侵權行為！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/t0oKqBSr9xaY2DLrbP_uso-mbj0=/802x745/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/DPSA6OSHH5C3RRQJRFFV7LYUPI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Ft0oKqBSr9xaY2DLrbP_uso-mbj0%3D%2F802x745%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FDPSA6OSHH5C3RRQJRFFV7LYUPI.jpg&h=1f9a5740&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍象香港的代理今日亦有在官方facebook專頁向『燉』發出聲明，內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n有關&lt;燉&gt;侵權藍象商標事項<br />\n<br />\n你好，<br />\n百利行環球有限公司 （「本公司」）為泰國藍象（Blue Elephant）產品的港澳總代理。近日收到泰國總部通知，發現 貴公司在未經授權的情況下使用其肖像（品牌名稱及其商標），並用於商業營銷，售賣與及宣傳一事。<br />\n為維護本公司及其品牌的合法權益，現發表聲明如下：<br />\n1. 本公司從未與貴司有過任何商業合作關係。<br />\n2. 本公司在這兩年內沒有收到貴司任何使用藍象（Blue Elephant)之肖像權/品牌/商標之申請。<br />\n現正發表嚴正聲明，敬請 貴司將所有包含與「藍象」相關的任何宣傳品，包括但不限於餐牌，Facebook/Instagram圖片，海報等移除，如在由今天起計兩星期後（3rd Feb 2020）繼續發現在餐廳內展示任何有關藍象品牌的宣稱，本公司必定會採取進一步行動，特此聲明！<br />\n百利行環球有限公司<br />\n2020年1月21日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/4zh1qqsxuUWtum1UQ1v2HvCZdYo=/802x1380/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/PYF536E4GC5KXUE2264HUB636U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F4zh1qqsxuUWtum1UQ1v2HvCZdYo%3D%2F802x1380%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FPYF536E4GC5KXUE2264HUB636U.jpg&h=841d9e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/7w-TP2pPqxgiXbmcC8P-InJXmz0=/802x612/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/CMZ34DN4K6KWZYNY72OU5HABJA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F7w-TP2pPqxgiXbmcC8P-InJXmz0%3D%2F802x612%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FCMZ34DN4K6KWZYNY72OU5HABJA.jpg&h=9822034f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b64603e336bda396c130d2f0710952ea0fba0c19","tid":1834086,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T08:58:56.000Z","msg":"手足連呢啲嘜頭都留意到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f479bb9893cc3597ef47623d7e5d00fa80d18782","tid":1834086,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:00:12.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"c49f669e48a6a00e008b07b193560d3e535887d1","tid":1834086,"uid":106276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717edc25c3214ddacdaaa0094d289f0ac2ebbd9e","tid":1834086,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T09:02:52.000Z","msg":"犯住法撐警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}